// cf.         The missing volume is probably the most important.
//             That is consistent with how archives behave when being difficult.
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------

/* <L1_VOICE> */
Licht      : "Books.
              Which is unfair."

Ad Libitum : "13 volumes confirmed present.
              Correction: 12 volumes confirmed present.
              One volume absent."

Licht      : "I cannot read any of this.

              ......

              Except this one line."

Ad Libitum : "You do not carry magi, Master.
              That is consistent with the inability to read."

Licht      : "I know.
              That is not what I said."

Ad Libitum : "...recording."

Licht      : "Partner."

Ad Libitum : "Master."

Licht      : "Be quiet.
              I am looking at it."
/* </L1_VOICE> */


